        <article class="clearfix">
            <div class="single-post indienova-single-post fr-view">
                <h4><strong>快速介绍</strong></h4><p>本周有两款较受关注的 FPS 游戏发售：</p><p>1、《狙击精英（Sniper Elite）》系列开发商 Rebellion 新作<a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/312670/Strange_Brigade/" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">《异域奇兵（Strange Brigade）》</a></p><p>2、《生存法则（survarium）》开发商 Vostok Games 新作<a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/819500/Fear_The_Wolves/" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">《恐惧狼群（Fear The Wolves）》</a></p><p>两款免费游戏：<a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/509580/The_Lord_of_the_Rings_Living_Card_Game/" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">指环王卡牌游戏</a>、画风可爱的 AVG <a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/917680/one_night_hot_springs/" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">one night, hot springs</a>，<a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/633230/NARUTO_TO_BORUTO_SHINOBI_STRIKER/" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">《火影忍者博人传:忍者先锋》</a>，世界上第一款 3DMMORPG 游戏 <a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/893390/Meridian_59/" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">Meridian 59</a> 的重制版。</p><h4><strong>Donut County</strong></h4><p>关键词：可爱、解谜、搞笑</p><p>发售日期：8月29日</p><p>&nbsp;六年！What Remains of Edith Finch 和 The Unfinished Swan 的设计者 Ben Esposito 的新作品 Donut County 终于要发售咯！由于开发周期很长，在未发售时就已经出现了 Hole.io 这样的模 chao 仿 xi 作品。本作支持中文。</p><p>参见站内文章<a href="https://indienova.com/indie-game-news/hole-io-copies-donut-county/" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">《Donut County 被抄：你选择快还是慢？》</a></p><p>本作中玩家扮演一个逐渐变大的地洞，把地上的东西丢进去，利用它解开谜题。还有很多可爱的角色们等着你！（比如那只浣熊）</p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2018/8/Donut County1.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="8840" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2018/8/Donut County2.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="8841" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2018/8/Donut County3.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="8842" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p class="hidden-xs"><iframe src="https://store.steampowered.com/widget/702670/" frameborder="0" style="width: 100%; height: 220px;"></iframe></p><h4><strong>Two Point Hospital</strong></h4><p>关键词：模拟、管理、欢乐</p><p>发售日期：8月30日</p><p>《主题医院》的精神续作！请这位病人不要死在过道上谢谢！</p><p>面对各种神秘罕见的疾病，开一家大医院吧！</p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2018/8/Two Point Hospital1.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="8843" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2018/8/Two Point Hospital2.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="8844" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2018/8/Two Point Hospital3.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="8845" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p class="hidden-xs"><iframe src="https://store.steampowered.com/widget/535930/" frameborder="0" style="width: 100%; height: 220px;"></iframe></p><h4><strong>Need to Know</strong></h4><p>关键词：反乌托邦、模拟、侦查</p><p>发售日期：8月29日</p><p>在一场恐怖分子渗透进核电站的灾难之后，一个新的情报机构诞生了，那就是你所处的自由部。监视那些责任人，窥探他们的私生活，确定他们是否具有威胁性。或者利用工作之便，来谋取一些个人利益？</p><p>本作暂无中文。</p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2018/8/Need to Know1.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="8874" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2018/8/Need to Know2.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="8875" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2018/8/Need to Know3.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="8876" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p class="hidden-xs"><iframe src="https://store.steampowered.com/widget/490930/" frameborder="0" style="width: 100%; height: 220px;"></iframe><br></p><h4><strong>Aggressors: Ancient Rome</strong></h4><p>关键词：策略、罗马、4X</p><p>发售日期：8月30日</p><p>本作暂无中文。重温历史，选择你的派系征服地中海各国！</p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2018/8/Aggressors Ancient Rome1.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="8846" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2018/8/Aggressors Ancient Rome2.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="8847" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2018/8/Aggressors Ancient Rome3.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="8848" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p class="hidden-xs"><iframe src="https://store.steampowered.com/widget/783210/" frameborder="0" style="width: 100%; height: 220px;"></iframe></p><h4><strong>The Messenger</strong></h4><p>关键词：像素、动作、平台</p><p>发售日期：8月30日</p><p>恶魔入侵，为了守护自己的村落，忍者踏上旅程！乍一看像是一款经典平台跳跃类游戏，但随后到来的却是充满惊险刺激和幽默元素的时光穿越之旅。</p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2018/8/The Messenger mini.gif" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="8849" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2018/8/The Messenger2.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="8850" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p class="hidden-xs"><iframe src="https://store.steampowered.com/widget/764790/" frameborder="0" style="width: 100%; height: 220px;"></iframe></p><h4><strong>Meow Wars: Card Battle</strong></h4><p>关键词：猫！、卡牌、联机</p><p>发售日期：8月31日</p><p>本作支持中文，游戏也有安卓和 ios 版。被画风吸引了所以推荐一下！（画师 Sam Moore 的 <a href="https://www.instagram.com/ugly_ink/" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">ins</a>）</p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2018/8/Meow Wars Card Battle1.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="8854" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2018/8/Meow Wars Card Battle2.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="8855" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p class="hidden-xs"><iframe src="https://store.steampowered.com/widget/762110/" frameborder="0" style="width: 100%; height: 220px;"></iframe></p><h4><strong>Shadows: Awakening &nbsp;暗影：觉醒</strong></h4><p>关键词：RPG、动作</p><p>发售日期：9月1日</p><p>本作支持中文。玩家扮演一个可以改变形态的恶魔，收集亡者灵魂，用五种不同的角色充实你的冒险。</p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2018/8/Shadows Awakening.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="8856" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2018/8/Shadows Awakening2.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="8857" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2018/8/Shadows Awakening3.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="8858" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p class="hidden-xs"><iframe src="https://store.steampowered.com/widget/585450/" frameborder="0" style="width: 100%; height: 220px;"></iframe></p><h4><strong>SFD</strong></h4><p>关键词：RPG、策略、地牢</p><p>发售日期：9月1日</p><p>暂无中文。一个有点硬核的 rogue-like 地牢+角色扮演游戏。在地牢中探索，用陷阱干掉怪物吧！</p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2018/8/SFD2.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="8860" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2018/8/SFD1.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="8859" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p class="hidden-xs"><iframe src="https://store.steampowered.com/widget/916040/" frameborder="0" style="width: 100%; height: 220px;"></iframe></p><h4><strong>Ruby &amp; Majesty: Treasure Team</strong></h4><p>关键词：像素、冒险、解谜</p><p>发售日期：9月1日</p><p>暂无中文。使用一对孪生英雄来解开谜题，按下所有的按钮，在时空的碎片中寻找永恒的宝藏！</p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2018/8/Ruby &amp; Majesty1.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="8861" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2018/8/Ruby &amp; Majesty2.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="8862" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2018/8/Ruby &amp; Majesty3.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="8863" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p class="hidden-xs"><iframe src="https://store.steampowered.com/widget/879520/" frameborder="0" style="width: 100%; height: 220px;"></iframe></p>
            </div>
